  "description": "<p>ASTEK has been providing IT and Engineering solutions for some of the world’s largest industrial and services groups for more than 35 years with 10,000 passionate experts in 22 countries throughout Europe, APAC, Middle East and the Americas</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Currently, we are looking for <strong>Java Developer </strong>which would be based in Singapore</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities and requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Bechelor Degree in Computer Science, Engineering, or a related field with minimum 5 years of experience in software development</li>\n  <li>Proven working experience in Java/J2EE application development</li>\n  <li>Strong knowledge of Java 8, Oracle, and PL/SQL including packages, views, procedures, etc.</li>\n  <li>Strong experience in WebLogic server</li>\n  <li>Working knowledge and experience with DevOps tools for source control and CI/CD, such as GitHub</li>\n</ul>",
